"ogimage":"http://s3-media2.ak.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/k96dOstP0NO0YE1OqLe3vg/l.jpg",
"rating":"5.0",
"reviewcomment":"The year was 1997...I was living in Italy at the time.  My sister and brother-in-law came to visit and we took the train up to Venice from Florence.<br>The month was August...what can I say....BOILING hot!!  We had been walking all day....our feet were killing us...we were hungry...<br>I referred to the DK Eyewitness Venice guidebook...thanks to this guidebook!!  We found Antica Besseta.<br><br>Now....this is 15 years ago...yes, we were hungry...but we had the best dinner.  The squid ink pasta was amazing...someone, I think my hubby (then boyfriend) had the pasta with crab....but everything was just so delicious....in between the courses, they served this palate cleansing pink coloured ice, served in a dainty glass on a white doily/white porcelain plate....well, all&#39;s a little blurry now, we started with glasses of Prosecco....we were tired and hungry....right, already typed that....<br><br>ALL four of us were extremely impressed.  We were all raised by parents who know what yumminess means....not in the snooty manner....<br><br>15 years later, we are still raving about them....recommending them to friends.  We hope to return for a meal soon...",
